        <item>
            <title>丹麥 B&#038;O 精選品味家居揚聲器，今個聖誕送一份超型禮物給至愛</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/bang-olufsen-chrismas-2023/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bang-olufsen-chrismas-2023</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/13/bang-olufsen-chrismas-2023/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技潮人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 03:07:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[b&o]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Bang & Olufsen]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1207747</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p2">快到聖誕，好多朋友都想送一份高貴典雅、又靚又實用的禮物給至愛，或者送一份禮物獎勵自己全年工作的努力。丹麥音響品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen (B&amp;O) 創立於 1925 年，作為丹麥王室家族御用品牌，他們一直推出極具品味、型格設計，同時具有專業鑑聽級質素的音響產品。今個聖誕想買一部樣靚而又好聲的喇叭，就要繼續留意下面介紹的三款 B&amp;O 精選喇叭產品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-scaled.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208126 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1066" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-scaled.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07541-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p class="p2">B&amp;O 在 11 月剛慶祝他們成立 98 週年，這個少數可以經歷這份長久歲月的音響品牌，其經典作品曾經被紐約現代藝術博物館 MoMa 作為永久展品。而面向現代音響科技發展，B&amp;O 結合了經典設計、出色的造工與時尚生活，推出一系列喇叭產品。</p><h2 class="p2">超輕薄設計精緻書本揚聲器<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>全新 Beosound Emerge</h2><p class="p2">這次重點介紹的是這部 B&amp;O Beosound Emerge 經典款入門級產品。設計用上書本式扁平設計，書脊位置用上鋁金屬物料，令高級感提升，加上喇叭厚度只有 6.7cm，看上去更像一本書，漫不經意地融入你的生活空間。即使在狹窄的香港居住空間中，仍能突顯你的生活品味。放在書架上，它馬上就同你的書架融為一體，也可放在廚房的角落、客廳的小桌上。而即使喇叭體積細小，但仍能發出足夠聲量，讓整個房間都被音樂包覆。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-rotated.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209537 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-600x900.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0008-rotated.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208121 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548.jpg" alt="" width="1067" height="1600" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548.jpg 1067w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07548-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1207764 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC07544-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">難能可貴的是這個尺寸的喇叭，仍可呈現出極廣闊的 180 度音響效果，令整個房間充滿音樂。極為輕薄的喇叭機身，Beosound Emerge 融合了由 B&amp;O 工程師精密調整的小型驅動器。驅動器採用特殊設計，包括了底部側放的 4 吋低音單元、中間傾斜擺放的輕巧型 1.45 吋中音驅動單元，還有裝在頂端向正面發聲的 0.6 吋高音單元，令喇叭面向任何方位，用家都可獲得 180 度全方位音樂體驗。用家可連接兩部 Beosound Emerge 使用 B&amp;O 智能電話 App 進行立體聲配對，享受更廣闊音場。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208125 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1229" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-694x533.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-1172x900.jpg 1172w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-768x590.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/螢幕截圖-2023-12-01-15.41.29-1-1536x1180.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208120 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p class="p2">除了實用好聲，B&amp;O 音響品牌更追求產品的耐用程度，Beosound Emerge 提供 3 年官方保養期，產品榮獲 Cradle to Cradle Certified 的 Bronze 認證，隨著聲音技術的不斷進化，用户可以在來年乃至未來數十年輕鬆為該產品升級。採用了尖端數碼管理平台 Mozart Platform 的揚聲器，確保了揚聲器日後升級，可迎合日新月異的全新音樂需求。</p><p class="p2"><strong>B&amp;O Beosound Emerge</strong></p><p class="p2"><strong>建議零售價：HK$5,598（3 年保養期）</strong></p><h2 class="p2">令整個家居變成音樂廳<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>碳黑色第 3 代 Beosound 2</h2><p class="p2">想突顯你的生活品味，這部 B&amp;O Beosound 2 3rd Gen 揚聲器將成為你家居中一件實用又型格的藝術品。Beosound 2 3rd Gen 家庭揚聲器可説是 B&amp;O 標誌性產品，在第三代更推出超型格碳黑新款。鋁金屬外殼，設計優雅之餘，支援多房間控制 (Multiroom) 功能，更可 360 度發聲，不論擺放在家中任何位置，都可令整個環境變成了廣闊的音樂空間。Beosound 2 3rd Gen 同樣採用 Mozart Platform 令它日後透過軟件升級加入更多新功能。</p><p class="p2"><strong>B&amp;O Beosound 2 第 3 代碳黑色</strong></p><p class="p2"><strong>建議零售價：HK$26,990（3 年保養期）</strong></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209541 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1920" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042.jpg 1067w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0042-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1209540 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0040-6