center size-medium wp-image-1209543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/unwire0072.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-694x419.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-694x419.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-1280x773.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-768x464.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-1536x927.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08141-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1209545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/KAN08137-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">上述介紹 3 款 B&amp;O 喇叭於 K11 MUSEA、ifc mall、銅鑼